<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your Signal Fire sign-in link</title>
  <style>
    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f2f0d9; font-family: "Instrument Sans", ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif; color: #1a1a12; }
    .wrapper { max-width: 560px; margin: 40px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; }
    .header { background-color: #1a1a12; padding: 32px 40px; }
    .header-label { font-family: "JetBrains Mono", ui-monospace, monospace; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #867a60; margin: 0 0 8px; }
    .header-title { font-family: "Instrument Serif", Georgia, serif; font-size: 28px; color: #f2f0d9; margin: 0; }
    .body { padding: 40px; }
    .greeting { font-size: 16px; margin: 0 0 20px; }
    .copy { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; color: #444; margin: 0 0 32px; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; background-color: #e24820; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 6px; }
    .note { font-size: 13px; color: #867a60; margin: 24px 0 0; }
    .footer { padding: 24px 40px; border-top: 1px solid #f2f0d9; font-size: 12px; color: #867a60; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <p class="header-label">Signal Fire</p>
      <h1 class="header-title">Your sign-in link.</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <p class="greeting">Hi<% if @user.name.present? %> <%= @user.name %><% end %>,</p>
      <p class="copy">
        Click below to sign in to Signal Fire. We'll let you know as soon as the mobile app launches.
      </p>
      <a href="<%= @magic_link %>" class="btn">Sign in to Signal Fire</a>
      <p class="note">This link expires in 30 minutes. If you didn't request this, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      Signal Fire &mdash; Community Play Tools, St. Petersburg, FL
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
